        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-10-15T17:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-07-28T18:00:00-05:00" n="195" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d195">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.J.18.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 74 bis</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00">undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>After Article 74, add a new article (74 bis), as follows: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“Italy shall forego any right to which she was entitled under any treaty
                            to be represented on or to participate in any commission of any kind
                            operating in Greece.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
